ShareAlike obligation: any redistributed knowledge-base table DERIVED from
NMRShiftDB2 -- e.g. the HOSE-code -> shift table produced by
scripts/build_hose_kb.py (and likewise a FAISS spectrum-similarity index or
embedding table produced by scripts/build_similarity_index.py) -- is a
